{"tid":696444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本土研：土地分配不均　有地都俾咗國際學校先？ 政府$1000批3.8公頃地俾哈羅國際學校","createTime":"2018-06-10T06:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T11:12:55.000Z","uid":48083,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9f8b7b5510d1ec4678e6af0e9e7b01423a703c92","tid":696444,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/10/141024_23f868b7a3c390994bc34b84594fb306.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F10%2F141024_23f868b7a3c390994bc34b84594fb306.png&h=2bc25324&s={SIZE}\" />近日傳出哈羅香港國際學校將低年級中文課程由繁轉簡，並解釋是「讓學生為2047年的香港做好準備」，引起嘩然。<br />\n <br />\n唔講唔知，原來哈羅幅地係2009年教育局分配出來，仲只以地價$1000批出！當你以為優惠價批地會是惠及民生社福機構，原來還包括這類「貴族學校」！<br />\n <br />\n自九七後，教育局主要有兩次批出全新土地予國際學校營辦團體，共批出七幅土地。名校兼帶動旁邊豪宅「名校效應」，完美成為地產項目推銷一部分。哈羅國際學校是邱德根兒子邱達強引入；另外獲批將軍澳峻瀅II旁地皮的英國名牌老校Shrewsbury International School，就是由陳智思引入。據報導，Shrewsbury International School Hong Kong Limited於2015年2月才成立，僅三個月就獲政府批地。當年加入成為董事的陳智思，亦被質疑未有向行政會議申報利益。<br />\n <br />\n不是要反對興建國際學校，但當學校以私校模式收取高昂學費(一般都每年過10萬元學費)，為何還需要政府以優惠地價來偏袒？另一邊廂，目前全港尚有廿多間自60年代起興建的「火柴盒校舍」小學，面積約3,000平方米或以下，日久失修，石屎剝落，政府卻懶撥資源協助，重置校舍遙遙無期。教育局有地，就不理這堆水深火熱的「火柴盒校舍」，反而先將資源撥給「貴族學校」！<br />\n<br />\n除此以外，成日話醫院､社福設施､各類院舍､公屋等等都缺乏用地，政府又只推說「造地不夠」。到底哪些用途較為逼切？<br />\n<br />\n真係要學許文彪一句：呢個世界公平咩？<br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n😉《好誠實研究》全文下載： <a href=\"http://www.landfordaycharmsheung.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.landfordaycharmsheung.hk&d=8rve7%2FShRofpxQpRRLTjD57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=0444bcde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.landfordaycharmsheung.hk</a><br />\n💰 集資印刷《好誠實研究》，一人捐$500、就可印多50本散落社區！<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2LgCPy6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LgCPy6&d=8rve7%2FShRofpxQpRRLTjD57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ec8271e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2LgCPy6</a><br />\n「民間土地資源小組」文集： <a href=\"https://medium.com/@citizenstaskforce.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40citizenstaskforce.hk%2F&d=8rve7%2FShRofpxQpRRLTjD57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=d40ecc58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@citizenstaskforce.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/244689185627162/posts/1823903511039047/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F244689185627162%2Fposts%2F1823903511039047%2F&d=8rve7%2FShRofpxQpRRLTjD57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=39cd87b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/244689185627162/posts/1823903511039047/</a>"},{"pid":"5db151e5144e7bb06ecbeba8257df9beeae8fe77","tid":696444,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:11:18.000Z","msg":"因為高級公務員仔女要讀呀"},{"pid":"8d36050c41830b28037d89f1b422f1b8dea9a500","tid":696444,"uid":31841,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"5db151e5144e7bb06ecbeba8257df9beeae8fe77","tid":696444,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:11:18.000Z","msg":"因為高級公務員仔女要讀呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:14:19.000Z","msg":"支那公務員仔女要讀咋"},{"pid":"184c03a6ac159ad528525f349253f5a711d835e3","tid":696444,"uid":127177,"like":1,"dislike":27,"score":-26,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:15:01.000Z","msg":"你都有官校讀啦，香港作為國際城市，點解唔可以劃分地俾國際學校辦學？又唔係無俾錢租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04ea843f34bcd2f6a8bbe6b81828897185a1414","tid":696444,"uid":48083,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"184c03a6ac159ad528525f349253f5a711d835e3","tid":696444,"uid":127177,"like":1,"dislike":27,"score":-26,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:15:01.000Z","msg":"你都有官校讀啦，香港作為國際城市，點解唔可以劃分地俾國際學校辦學？又唔係無俾錢租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:15:38.000Z","msg":"3.8公頃收$1000？？"},{"pid":"2100e2b786c477b65a6ce131981c58852d3968e5","tid":696444,"uid":164730,